<法規內容>
  <條文>
    <條號>Article 1</條號>
    <條文內容><![CDATA[These Standards are issued under the authority of Paragraph 2, Article 19 of the Dental Technicians Act (hereinafter referred to as the Act).
]]></條文內容>
  </條文>
  <條文>
    <條號>Article 2</條號>
    <條文內容><![CDATA[Dental laboratories shall be able to provide the dental laboratory work stipulated in Paragraph 2, Article 12 of the Act.
]]></條文內容>
  </條文>
  <條文>
    <條號>Article 3</條號>
    <條文內容><![CDATA[Any establishment of a dental laboratory shall comply with the following requirements:
1. Personnel: shall meet the qualification requirements of Paragraph 2, Article 18 of the Act for prospective laboratories
2. Facilities including:
i. A clearly delineated, independent operating facility
ii. Clearly defined finished product areas, along with cleaning equipment, waste treatment equipment, fume and dust extraction equipment, and metal and plaster grinders
iii. Appropriate ventilation, dust prevention and lighting equipment
iv. Such other equipment as may be needed for the professional practice of dental laboratory work and systems to preserve the operating records
3. Other:
i. A total floor area of not less than 20 sq. m.
ii. Where the dental laboratory will share space at the same address with another healthcare practice, there shall be clearly delineated independent means of egress and ingress.
]]></條文內容>
  </條文>
  <條文>
    <條號>Article 4</條號>
    <條文內容><![CDATA[These Standards shall take effect immediately from the date of promulgation.
]]></條文內容>
  </條文>
</法規內容>
